    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini dei eterni, anno hab (sic) incarnatione eius millesimo
                        centesimo LXIII, sesta kal. decembris, inditione duodecima. Manifesti sumus
                        nos <persName>Bonifatius</persName> et <persName>Buiamonte</persName>
                        germani filii quondam <persName ref="#people/3227">Uguicioni</persName>
                        <persName>Bonifatii</persName> et uxoris eius <persName>Cangniola</persName>
                        filia <persName>Guiduci</persName> et <persName>Giemma</persName> filia
                            <persName>Aldobrandi</persName>, anbo iste interrogate sunt a
                                <persName><name ref="Piculus">Picculo</name></persName> iudice, (…)
                        quia per hanc cartulam venditionis vindimus et tradimus<orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206">
                            <rs key="#Hospitals">iosspitale</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                            >Altipasti</placeName></orgName> venerabili loco in manum
                            <persName>Montanini</persName> rectori osspitalis idem una petia de
                        terra que est posita in loco qui vocatur Prata in <rs
                            key="#Seigneurial_district">curte</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/3210"
                            key="#Roads #Seigneurial_district">Puteo</placeName>. Tamen decernimus
                        terram petia ipsa cuide una parte est fini terre del
                            <persName>Vecchio</persName> et <persName>Alchiruoli</persName>. De
                        secunda parte est fini terre <persName>Bonardi</persName>. De tertia parte
                        est fini terre <persName>Adimari</persName> et
                            <persName>Guidalocti</persName>. De quarta parte est fini terra <rs
                            key="#Roads">via pubblica</rs> currit. Ideo predicta petia terra novem
                        staiora ad iusta pertica misurata, unum panorum et medium mino (…) vendimus
                        et tradimus (…). Pro ipsa venditione nostram (sic) recepimus nos (…) inter
                        argentum et alias mobilias prova valiente libre novem et sol. XII de bonis
                        denaris de Lucca et di Pisa. (…). <foreign>Pena</foreign>: dupplum. (…)
                        Actum <placeName ref="#places/3227">Gangalandi</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/83">florentino</geogName>. Signum
                        manum supradictorum iugalium (…). Signa manuum <persName>Salamoni</persName>
                        filius <persName>Guidi Mariole</persName> et <persName>Guidocti</persName>
                        filius <persName>Tancridi</persName> et <persName>Orlandini
                            Moricti</persName> et <persName>Zoppi Moricti</persName> et
                                <persName><name>Martinelli</name> de Puteo</persName>, qui ibidem
                        fuerunt rogati testes. (S) Ego Picculus notarius post tradita dicta
                        complevi. <persName><name>Falco</name></persName> rogavi sta (sic) cartula
                        et recepi in sua manum a vice osspitium Altipasti. </ab>
                </div>
